   115→## API Reference
   117→### Types
   119→- `MCPHost` - Main SDK type
   120→- `Options` - Configuration options
   121→- `Message` - Conversation message
      →…
   124→### Methods
   126→- `New(ctx, opts)` - Create new MCPHost instance
   127→- `Prompt(ctx, message)` - Send message and get response
   128→- `PromptWithCallbacks(ctx, message, ...)` - Send message with progress callbacks
      →…
   136→## Environment Variables
   138→All CLI environment variables work with the SDK:
   139→
   140→- `MCPHOST_MODEL` - Override model
   141→- `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` - Anthropic API key
   142→- `OPENAI_API_KEY` - OpenAI API key
   143→- `GEMINI_API_KEY` - Google API key
   144→- etc.
   145→
   146→## License
   148→Same as MCPHost CLI

